headline: State Street Announces Enterprise Performance is Now Live
summary: BOSTON, September 24, 2025--State Street Corporation announced today, through its Charles River Development business, that Enterprise Performance, powered by Opturo速, is now live for clients of the Charles River Investment Management Solution (IMS) and State Street Alpha速. The fully integrated solution offers a single performance calculation engine that enables greater efficiency in performance operations.
